Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0) applies to the benchmark case adaptations, metadata, schema, and documentation created for this repository, unless otherwise noted.

Adapted-real cases are paraphrased and condensed benchmark artifacts derived from public source documents. Original source documents remain governed by their own licenses, terms, and rights. Source URLs and provenance are included for traceability. This dataset does not relicense the underlying source documents.

Clinical, legal, tax, regulatory, cloud-operations, immigration, housing, and institutional policy examples are evaluation artifacts only and are not professional guidance.
